    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "周都督观水寨忽发旧症，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这件事倒叫我难以调停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕的是奸曹贼趁此偷营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正在军务吃紧之时，都督忽得重病，这便如何是好？我不免去寻诸葛先生，倘"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若能治都督之病，岂不是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里出大营把诸葛来请，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        1.0,
        0.6667,
        0.3333,
        0.0,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.6667,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "诸葛亮",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "昨夜晚观天象阴阳料定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹孟德众人马尽被火攻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为的是初冬时缺少东风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看一看周公瑾是怎样施行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急急忙忙往前走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又只见先生在船头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，大夫来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫请坐。大夫不在营中与周都督共参军务，来到江边做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生有所不知，只因我家都督，忽染大病，当此军务要紧之时，不久就要与曹"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵交战，是我特来与先生商议。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公瑾之病，山人却能医治。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，先生若能将我家都督病体治好，不但我鲁肃感激于你，就是我主吴侯，也"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是感恩非浅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此大夫带路，就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "遭不幸天降灾公瑾染病，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还得要仗先生妙手回春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫大夫你与我忙把路引，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管叫你周都督疾病离身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮、鲁肃同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "诸葛亮→鲁肃",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
          "edge": "鲁肃→诸葛亮",
          "turns": 5
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 3,
          "白": 8
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.273,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮原板",
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
