    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周瑜",
        "诸葛亮",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二旗牌搀周瑜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望破曹军大功可定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又谁知天不佑难遂人心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨天公不由我愁闷在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮随鲁肃同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请得良医到，进帐说分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：诸葛先生到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说吾有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请诸葛先生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督在哪里？吓，参见都督。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瑜染病在身，未能远迎，望先生恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告坐。请问都督：贵体欠安，未知因何而起？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想是瑜才拙意笨，连日军事匆忙，又感风寒，以至旧疾复作。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此所谓天有不测的风云，人有旦夕的祸福，但不知都督胸中怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是胸中膨闷得紧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此病必须理气，气顺，则病自除。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就请先生赐一良方，待瑜试服一二剂如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若要治病，必须先知病源。待山人先开一服案，请都督观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫看笔墨伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。诸葛亮写。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请都督看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“长江水战，大破曹兵；安排妙计，专用火攻；万事俱备，只欠东风！”"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀先生啊！你今将我心事猜透，务祈先生看在国事为重，速设良谋，瑜感恩"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非浅！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督但放宽心。亮自幼曾遇异人传授呼风唤雨，今日事既至此，亮当略试其技。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望都督差人，在南屏山下高筑一台，名曰“七星坛”。台凡三层，每层高五"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丈。第一层上设五色旗帜二十八面，以应二十八宿，用看台兵四名、童子十二"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名，伺候拈香拜斗等事；第二层用红旗六面、黑旗七面共一十三面，以应南北"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斗之势，亦用看台兵四名、童子十二名；第三层用黑白旗八面，以应乾、坎、"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "艮、震、巽、离、坤、兑八卦之象，用看台兵四名、童子十二名。不得有鸡犬、"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妇人之声。山人披发仗剑、诵咒祈祷。自本月二十一日甲子酉时起风，至二"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十三日丙寅之日风息。有三昼夜的东风，谅都督定必足用了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢说三昼夜，只须一夜东风，大功即可成就了。就命大夫速速筑造起来，一夜"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定要告竣，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此一番南屏山把东风祭定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕的是小周郎又起杀心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮下。鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "南屏山筑高台连夜造起，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "准备那诸葛亮祷告神祗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高台明日即可造成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那孔明口出狂言，难道他真有呼风唤雨之能么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人博学多能，善会奇门遁甲，都督不可轻视于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他倘能如此多能，日后东吴定受其害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔明吓，孔明！我不杀你，誓不为人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那孔明博学问惊天动地，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "专奇门习遁甲晓畅兵机；"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我定要差兵将将他杀之！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周瑜下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "周都督虽聪敏心太嫉妒，"
        }
      ],
