      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引周瑜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急欲破曹军，昼夜不安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，外面风起，待我看来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，果然东南风大起。这诸葛亮真有巧夺造化、翻覆阴阳之力！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，传丁奉、徐盛进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丁奉、徐盛进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐盛 （内同白） 来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丁奉、徐盛同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁奉、徐盛",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你二人去至南屏山，将诸葛亮杀来见我！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁奉、徐盛",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丁奉、徐盛同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传蒋钦、周泰进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒋钦、周泰进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周泰 （内同白） 来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒋钦、周泰同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋钦、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去至江岸，若遇孔明，将他杀死，即是尔等第一大功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋钦、周泰",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒋钦、周泰同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！众将官！吩咐满台大小三军，饱餐战饭，全身披挂，准备大破曹兵者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。周瑜下。）"
